A shocking new video appearing to show at least 30 Christians being beheaded and shot by ISIS in Libya has been released .
The 29-minute video shows dozens of militants holding two separate groups captive , thought to be in the south and the west of the country .
At least 16 men described by Islamic State as the ` followers of the cross from the enemy Ethiopian Church ' are lined up and shot in a desert .
This follows another video in February of the beheading of a group of 21 Coptic Christians on the beach in Libya .